{"tid":387451,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人都係中意自己一個？","createTime":"2017-09-04T15:35:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-08T18:33:52.000Z","uid":143838,"like":42,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3e779a9941e840651e12a8223f5d6bd92c1a8ea0","tid":387451,"uid":143838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T15:35:41.000Z","msg":"上到大學啲fd好難交到心 好難keep到contact <br />\n可能只係岩岩開始未適應<br />\n但諗諗下自己一個真係幾好<br />\n表面上好似中意一班人玩 但實際上中意自己一個摺獨<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb0519206639cbfab1863d658444c6c38d8cc19c","tid":387451,"uid":137495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T15:37:55.000Z","msg":"自己一個整理下思緒係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自己一個靜下 冇人煩都好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n摺成世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fadd491b1aaa8153465c4855658b323f306c80e5","tid":387451,"uid":143173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T15:40:07.000Z","msg":"你唔係摺得好緊要 正正常常到時點都會有人撩你既"},{"pid":"a7d4e0e8fab0b55848e4ebac6435d0dfbd971819","tid":387451,"uid":73909,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T15:41:05.000Z","msg":"自己一個係最舒服"},{"pid":"e84658f9b69b8a04eeac3d660a8d1cb0bf3d6191","tid":387451,"uid":143838,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T15:42:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自己一個整理下思緒係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自己一個靜下 冇人煩都好正<img sr